    <text>
        <body>
            <div>
                <head>Translated parts</head>
                <p xml:id="CH1a0930-start">
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-1a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-01-02T00:13:41.761+09:00">Situated between Heaven and Earth,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-1a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-01-02T00:14:07.839+09:00">sages study the past to guide people. I.1.1</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-1a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-01-02T00:14:27.405+09:00">They observe the opening and the closing of yin and yang to name things,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-1a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-01-02T00:14:57.125+09:00">to know the gateway to life and death, to manage the beginning and theending of a myriad of things,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-1a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-01-02T00:15:23.724+09:00">and to understand the human heart1 andways of thinking.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-1a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-01-02T00:15:47.841+09:00">Able to detect signs of change, they guard the gatewayto the myriad of things.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-1a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-01-02T00:16:19.494+09:00">From the past to the present, the sages live amongpeople and always keep their Dao (道)2 consistent.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-1a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-01-02T00:16:39.499+09:00">Countless changes are governed by their respective laws and purposes.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-1a.16" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-01-02T00:17:09.258+09:00">They are all either yin or yang,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-1a.17" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-01-02T00:17:49.973+09:00">soft or hard,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-1a.18" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-01-02T00:17:59.224+09:00">open or shut,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-1a.19" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-01-02T01:05:28.264+09:00">loose or tight.</seg>
                </p>
